What will a Zoo Bring？ 
动物园能带来什么？

Mix used center, open space for whole city, international zoo for world. 
混合功能中心，北京市的城市公园，世界性的动物园

People  come  here  because  they  can  stay  with  animals,  they  can  be 
close  with  nature,  they  can  have  some  entertainment,  they  can  live, 
they can work, they can go shopping... 

Beijing  citizens  rarely  go  to  the  current  zoo,  but  they  will  go  to  the  new 
one because it is a riverside open space. 
北京居民很少去动物园，但如果这里成了一个城市公园，将吸引更多的人前来

